Galmar Stone-Fist
High Concept: The Iron Hand of the Rebellion, The Old Bear
Race: Nord
Standing Stone: The Lord (Resilience and Armor)
Power Level: Legendary Hero (Apex Warlord Build)
"I fought for the Empire. I bled for it. And when I came home, I found elves telling me who to worship in my own house. Never again."

Appearance: The Living Monument
Galmar is a mountain of a man, broad-shouldered and scarred. His beard is braided with bone beads, and his eyes are the color of flint. He wears the distinctive bear-pelt armor of a Stormcloak General, but it is reinforced with custom steel plating. He moves with the heavy, inevitable momentum of a glacier. He does not carry magic items; he carries steel that has been cared for so well it shines like silver.

