V. Combat Tactics
The Warlord: Galmar leads from the front. He is an Anchor.
Opening: He uses Battle Cry to scatter weaker enemies, then charges the biggest threat on the field (Ulag).
The Duel: He wants to lock the enemy boss in single combat. He uses The Bear's Verdict to crush defenses.
Support: He expects his allies to flank while he holds the enemy's attention. He will shout tactical orders ("Flank him! Keep the archers off me!").



